  <exercise label="mucp_15_9" numbered="yes" adaptive="yes" indentation="hide">
    <statement>
      <p>Let's write the <c>struct</c> definition for a <c>Matrix</c>! The underlying
            data structure is a <c>vector</c> of <c>vector</c>s of <c>int</c>s. Write
            the constructor and <c>at</c> function, which returns the data stored
